sentences: Jan Erik Tiwaz, aka Tyr (born 22 June 1972) is the former bassist for the Norwegian black/folk metal band Borknagar.

Jan Erik Tiwaz, aka Tyr (born 22 June 1972) is the former bassist for the Norwegian black/folk metal band Borknagar.
He currently resides in Drammen, Norway.
During June 2010, an announcement was released that due to "general disagreements", Jan Erik Tiwaz left Borknagar.
